It sounds like there may be an issue with the chat name not displaying properly in the sidebar of your app. This could be due to a delay in updating the chat history or a caching issue. 

One potential solution is to check the code responsible for updating the chat name in the sidebar. Make sure that the function to display the chat name is being called correctly and that the necessary data is being passed to it.

Additionally, you may want to look into any caching mechanisms in your app that could be preventing the chat name from updating in real-time. Clearing the cache or implementing a mechanism to force a reload of the sidebar when a new chat is initiated could help resolve the issue.
